checkout `https://github.com/homebase/php-tools` somewhere
run `./install all`
create symlink: `ln -s $TOOLS_PATH/php-tools/bin tools`

In order to have executable spartan tests you need to place `stest` symlink into your PATH 

you can add `tools` directory or create symlinks in `~/bin` or `/usr/local/bin`

@see [php-tools README](https://github.com/homebase/php-tools#install) file for more details
